PrecisAmendments to the CUSTOMS SUFFERANCE WAREHOUSES REGULATIONS which add provisions to allow the Minister to establish warehouse physical security requirements, identify high risk goods as forfeit if not removed within prescribed time limits and remove record-keeping provisions.
